<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="suddenly-adv">suddenly <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sʌdənli/    美 /'sʌdənli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>突然地；意外地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We were about to leave there when it began to rain heavily and suddenly. 
就在我们要离开时，突然下起了大雨。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>We were talking on the phone when, <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (突然), the line went dead.  （2007 陕西改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. suddenly  </p></div>